nodes.text: Goran was a Human male who served as a corporal in the Republic Army during the Cold War. Assigned to Search and Rescue Squad 204 on the planet Taris, Goran served under Sergeant Elara Dorne. When the squad showed up to rescue captured Republic soldiers from the Fallenspire Stronghold on Taris, Elara ordered Goran to guard the exit from the bunker.
